 And why don't we stretch out our hands?

17
00:00:45,600 --> 00:00:46,600
 Let's pray.

18
00:00:46,600 --> 00:00:51,640
 Father, I'm very grateful for Ellison, Brittany, Isaiah, for this family amongst us.

19
