 And we pray that You would come by Your Spirit and just teach us today, both through the

23
00:01:10,680 --> 00:01:16,760
 Scriptures but also through Ellison's example in his life of how we can be better equipped

24
00:01:16,760 --> 00:01:20,400
 to serve the most important relationships that are around us.

25
00:01:20,400 --> 00:01:22,400
 And we thank You for this in Jesus' name.

26
